<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/iconoir-icons/iconoir@main/css/iconoir.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        main {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .project {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            padding-bottom: 2rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        
        .project:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .project h3 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .project-meta {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .project-description {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .project-tech {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .project-tags {
            display: inline-flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-left: 0.5rem;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        
        .tag {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: #666;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            cursor: help;
        }
        
        .tag:hover {
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .tag i {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        .tag .tooltip {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 100%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            white-space: nowrap;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }
        
        .tag .tooltip::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 100%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            border: 4px solid transparent;
            border-top-color: #333;
        }
        
        .tag:hover .tooltip {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        
        a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .contact {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .contact a {
            margin: 0 1rem;
            color: #666;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .contact a:hover {
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .contact i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Your Name</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Software Developer / Designer / Your Title</p>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section class="section">
            <h2>About</h2>
            <p>A brief introduction about yourself, your skills, and what you do.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="section">
            <h2>Projects</h2>
            <div id="projects-container">
            <div class="project">
                <h3>termkit<span class="project-tags"><span class="tag"><i class="iconoir-user"></i><span class="tooltip">Author</span></span><span class="tag"><i class="iconoir-book"></i><span class="tooltip">Documentation</span></span><span class="tag"><i class="iconoir-refresh-circle"></i><span class="tooltip">Active</span></span></span></h3>
                <p class="project-meta">Jun 2024 | <a href="https://github.com/tylercritchlow/termkit" target="_blank">GitHub</a></p>
                <p class="project-description">A set of drop in terminal widgets made in Rust.</p>
                <p class="project-tech"><strong>Technologies:</strong> Rust</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <h3>Flux<span class="project-tags"><span class="tag"><i class="iconoir-user"></i><span class="tooltip">Author</span></span><span class="tag"><i class="iconoir-refresh-circle"></i><span class="tooltip">Active</span></span></span></h3>
                <p class="project-meta">Jan 2024 | <a href="https://github.com/tylercritchlow/Flux" target="_blank">GitHub</a></p>
                <p class="project-description">My own pure Rust version control system</p>
                <p class="project-tech"><strong>Technologies:</strong> Rust</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <h3>vexel</h3>
                <p class="project-meta">Feb 2025 | <a href="https://github.com/tylercritchlow/vexel" target="_blank">GitHub</a></p>
                <p class="project-description">Linear algebra library</p>
                <p class="project-tech"><strong>Technologies:</strong> Rust</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <h3>bevy<span class="project-tags"><span class="tag"><i class="iconoir-git-merge"></i><span class="tooltip">Contributor</span></span><span class="tag"><i class="iconoir-check-circle"></i><span class="tooltip">Has Tests</span></span><span class="tag"><i class="iconoir-code"></i><span class="tooltip">Examples</span></span><span class="tag"><i class="iconoir-book"></i><span class="tooltip">Documentation</span></span></span></h3>
                <p class="project-meta">May 2025 | <a href="https://bevyengine.org" target="_blank">View Project</a> | <a href="https://github.com/tylercritchlow/bevy" target="_blank">GitHub</a></p>
                <p class="project-description">A refreshingly simple data-driven game engine built in Rust</p>
                <p class="project-tech"><strong>Technologies:</strong> Rust</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <h3>rancher-desktop</h3>
                <p class="project-meta">Jun 2025 | <a href="https://rancherdesktop.io" target="_blank">View Project</a> | <a href="https://github.com/tylercritchlow/rancher-desktop" target="_blank">GitHub</a></p>
                <p class="project-description">Container Management and Kubernetes on the Desktop</p>
                <p class="project-tech"><strong>Technologies:</strong> TypeScript</p>
            </div>
                <!-- Projects will be added here -->
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer class="contact">
        <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com" title="Email">
            <i class="iconoir-mail"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" title="GitHub">
            <i class="iconoir-github"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" title="LinkedIn">
            <i class="iconoir-linkedin"></i>
        </a>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
